This is the bblfish branch of the Apache version of Clerezza ( http://clerezza.org/ ).
This branch is geared towards Social Web development as explained by http://bblfish.net/ 
Please clone the github repository and notify https://github.com/bblfish/clerezza
of changes you want integrated.

It currently requires following three Web Request Handler API projects to be built first, until the patches find their way back to their main repositories. 

$ git clone git@github.com:bblfish/wymiwyg-wrhapi.git
$ cd wymiwyg-wrhapi.git
$ mvn clean install -Dgpg.skip=true 

$ git clone git@github.com:bblfish/wymiwyg-wrhapi-osgi.git
$ cd wymiwyg-wrhapi-osgi
$ mvn clean install -Dgpg.skip=true 

$ git clone git@github.com:bblfish/wymiwyg-wrhapi-jetty.git
$ cd wymiwyg-wrhapi-jetty
$ mvn clean install -Dgpg.skip=true -Dmaven.test.skip=true

Java7 should be used for development here.

